ActTelefilm Canada Act
PrecisAppointment, effective August 23, 2004, of CAROLLE BRABANT of Montréal, Quebec, to act as Executive Director of Telefilm Canada, during pleasure, in the stead of Richard Stursberg, who has resigned, until such time as an executive director is appointed.
